    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Solid value and ready to roll! This car is in fair condition \u2014 it's a dependable, drivable vehicle that gets the job done, though it does show some noticeable wear and may have a few minor mechanical or cosmetic quirks that come with its age and use. Nothing that should scare away a practical buyer looking for honest, everyday transportation at a reasonable price. If you're after a no-frills, functional ride without breaking the bank, this one deserves a look!",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Here's a practical, budget-friendly opportunity for the savvy buyer! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it starts up reliably and handles everyday driving without major drama. You'll notice some cosmetic wear and a few minor imperfections that come with regular use, but nothing that gets in the way of getting you where you need to go. It's a solid choice for a commuter who wants dependable transportation at an accessible price point \u2014 come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make any decisions. The exterior shows visible signs of use \u2014 expect several scratches, scuffs, and minor dents across the body panels, and the paint has faded in certain areas. The interior is functional but worn: the upholstery has noticeable wear, there are some stains on the seats, and a few trim pieces show cracking or discoloration. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a solid opportunity for a buyer who is handy, looking for a project, or simply needs reliable basic transportation without paying a premium price.",
      "price": 20500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and I want to give you the full, honest picture of what that means. This car is in exceptional, like-new condition \u2014 it presents beautifully both inside and out, with no mechanical issues, no warning lights, and a clean, pristine interior free of tears, stains, or odors. The exterior is equally impressive, showing no dents, scratches, or paint imperfections, and all glass, trim, and lights are in perfect working order. The engine runs smoothly and quietly, all systems function as intended, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. If you're looking for a car that feels as close to driving off the lot as possible without paying new-car prices, this is it \u2014 a truly turn-key purchase with nothing left to fix, replace, or worry about.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "terse_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "terse_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition with significant wear and mechanical issues, best suited for a buyer prepared to invest in repairs.",
